If you have already read the help on the events sytem (?events) then
for examples what I'd recommend doing is running around looking at
room's event hooks...  do:

    @d here&lt;$event_handler&gt;,
    @d me&lt;$event_handler&gt;,

=46rom there, follow the referenced objects.  Just look at the
=2Eevent_notify methods on the given objects to see what they are doing
with the events listed as symbols.  A place to start would be the Pit
on the Cold Dark and Squeak.

-Brandon

